<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Facture</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica', 'Arial', sans-serif;
            font-size: 10px;
            margin: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }
        .header, .info, .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #fff;
            background-color: #3498db;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 10px;
        }
        .header-section {
            display: inline-block;
            vertical-align: top;
            width: 49%;
        }
        .header-section p {
            margin: 2px 0;
        }
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            font-size: 9px;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
        th {
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 5px;
        }
        td {
            padding: 5px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            text-align: right;
        }
        td:first-child {
            text-align: left;
        }
        .totals td {
            font-weight: bold;
            border: none;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }
        .footer p {
            font-size: 8px;
            color: #999;
        }
        .payment-info, .signateur_client {
            font-size: 9px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .payment-info a, .payment-info p {
            margin: 3px 0;
        }
        .signateur {
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            height: 50px;
            width: 200px;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Facture</h1>
        <div class="header-section">
            <p><strong>N°:</strong> {{invoiceInfo.invoiceNumber}}</p>
            <p><strong>Date de création:</strong> {{ invoiceInfo.createdAt|date('d/m/Y') }}</p>
            <p><strong>Échéance au:</strong> {{ invoiceInfo.dueDate|date('d/m/Y') }}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="header-section">
            <p><strong>Nom:</strong> {{ client.lastName }}</p>
            <p><strong>Adresse:</strong> {{ client.address }}</p>
            <p><strong>Email:</strong> {{ client.email }}</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="info">
        <p><strong>Nom Entreprise:</strong> {{ companyInfo.name }}</p>
        <p><strong>Adresse:</strong> {{ companyInfo.address }}</p>
        <p><strong>Téléphone:</strong> {{ companyInfo.phone }}</p>
    </div>

    <table>
        <thead>
        <tr>
            <th>Produit</th>
            <th>Quantité</th>
            <th>Prix unitaire (HT)</th>
            <th>TVA%</th>
            <th>Total (HT)</th>
            <th>Total (TTC)</th>
        </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
        {% for product in productList %}
            <tr>
                <td>{{ product.product.name }}</td>
                <td>{{ product.quantity }}</td>
                <td>{{ product.unitPrice }}</td>
                <td>{{ product.product.VAT }}</td>
                <td>{{ product.THT }}</td>
                <td>{{ product.TTC }}</td>
            </tr>
        {% endfor %}
        <tr class="totals">
            <td colspan="5" style="text-align: right;"><strong>Total HT:</strong></td>
            <td>{{ invoiceInfo.totalHT }} €</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="totals">
            <td colspan="5" style="text-align: right;"><strong>Total TTC:</strong></td>
            <td>{{ invoiceInfo.totalTTC }} €</td>
        </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>

    <div class="payment-info">
        <p><strong>Informations de paiement:</strong></p>
        <p>Nous acceptons les paiements par virement bancaire. Veuillez choisir votre méthode de paiement :</p>
        <p><strong>Payer en ligne</strong></p>
        <p><a href="{{ url('payment_full', {'id': invoiceInfo.id}) }}">Payer la totalité</a> | <a href="{{ url('payment_installments', {'id': invoiceInfo.id}) }}">Payer en plusieurs fois</a> | <a href="{{ url('payment_deposit', {'id': invoiceInfo.id}) }}">Payer un acompte</a></p>
        <p><strong>Payer en chèque :</strong></p>
        <p>Libellez votre chèque à l'ordre de Fast Invoice et envoyez-le à l'adresse suivante :</p>
        <p>Fast Invoice<br>242 Rue du Faubourg Saint-Antoine, Paris (75012)</p>
    </div>

    <div class="signateur_client">
        <p><strong>Signature client:</strong></p>
        <div class="signateur"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>Conditions générales de vente | Politique de confidentialité</p>
        <p>&copy; 2024 {{ companyInfo.name }}. Tous droits réservés.</p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
